data.description:
Care Free Twin Home Living!  This spacious twin home offers 4 bedrooms and 3 baths.  Your foyer welcomes you into a living room with a gas fireplace and dining area.  The kitchen has a center island that overlooks the great room area. It has a breakfast bar, table eating and a walk-in pantry. The primary bedroom is located on the main floor with a private full bath.  The main floor also has a guest bedroom and full guest bath. Your lower level has a spacious family room, two additional bedrooms and 3/4 bath.  You can enjoy the sauna located in the lower bath.  You will also appreciate all the storage available.
The sale includes a custom entertainment center, custom desk, bar stools, etc..Buyer does need to be over 50 yr old or older to purchase.
